lead_paragraph: No one will have savoured the fact that Middlesbrough's 1-1 draw with Manchester City at the Etihad Stadium followed just four days after Barcelona's 3-1 defeat there more than visiting manager Aitor Karanka.

headline.print_headline: Ole! Boro Manager Karanka Savours Special Moment at City
